E1%BA%A3-Ch%C3%AD/author-czNgfqjBLDLN86oT7B_L9g">Giả Chí</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-m8buZGd9acbui1906QmgWA">Thanh Tâm tài nhân tập tự - 青心才人詩集序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/author-ZpBj6D9P3q-U3JR36g_w5g">Chu Mạnh Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%B1-Nh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%A2y-kinh-ph%C3%AC-th%E1%BA%A3-di-c%C6%B0-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93n-mao-%E1%BB%91c-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-DX-pDiZIU7R1XM7QPDrBlw">Tự Nhương Tây kinh phì thả di cư Đông Đồn mao ốc kỳ 3 - 自瀼西荊扉且移居東屯茅屋其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%E1%BB%A8c-c%E1%BB%B1u-du-k%C3%BD-Ti%E1%BB%81u-qu%E1%BA%ADn-Nguy%C3%AAn-tham-qu%C3%A2n/poem-t2FLnp1OUcGOzN8rzYFlxQ">Ức cựu du ký Tiều quận Nguyên tham quân - 憶舊游寄譙郡元參軍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
